---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy — LocalResizer" description="LocalResizer privacy policy. Your files never leave your device.">
  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16 prose prose-slate">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p><em>Last updated: March 2026</em></p>
    <h2>The Short Version</h2>
    <p><strong>Your files never leave your device.</strong> All image processing happens 100% in your browser using client-side JavaScript. We do not upload, store, or transmit your images to any server.</p>
    <h2>What We Collect</h2>
    <p>We use minimal analytics to understand how our tool is used:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Page views and general usage patterns (via privacy-respecting analytics)</li>
      <li>No personal information is collected</li>
      <li>No cookies are used for tracking</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>What We Don't Collect</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Your images or files — they never leave your browser</li>
      <li>Personal information, names, or email addresses</li>
      <li>File names, metadata, or content of any kind</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>We may display advertisements through Google AdSense. Google may use cookies to serve ads based on your prior visits. You can opt out of personalized advertising at <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Google Ads Settings</a>.</p>
    <h2>Changes</h2>
    <p>We may update this policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated date.</p>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions about this policy? Visit our <a href="/contact">contact page</a>.</p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
